INSERT INTO `faqs` VALUES (2,'What is Olive?','Olive is a App that provides coupons, offers, and deals on various local stores, restaurants, bars, cafes, hotels, water parks, theaters, amusement parks, shopping stores etc. Olive ensures that the customers get the right deals and exclusive offers to save on every purchase. Customers can use these coupon codes and buy their desired product at a much lower price.\r\nThere are similar stores which will provide you with matching options. But we at Olive provide more excellent and better offers to our valuable customers/users so they can benefit the most.',1,'2022-07-18 02:08:06','2022-07-26 16:17:34'),(3,'How do I find saving in my area?','Olive app has two easy ways to quickly access local offers:\r\n 1.Download our mobile app! The Olive Mobile App brings you all our offers wherever       you are.  Simply search for Olive-offer live on Apples App Store or Google Play and install it.\r\n 2. Register you self! \r\n Simply Login with your user name and contact no and verify with OTP and enjoy instant access to all the offers in your smart phone',1,'2022-07-26 17:09:12','2022-07-26 17:09:12'),(4,'Can I search for offers outside my area using the app?','Absolutely! Simply go into the apps search and youll then be prompted to enter the area name or pincode youd like to search.When youre done,just change the setting back to current Location to go back to searching offers in your area.',1,'2022-07-26 17:09:46','2022-07-26 17:09:46'),(5,'Can I convert my coupon or benefit to hard cold cash?','Sorry, that feature is not available. But, you can always redeem it at the stores only for exciting offers ad deals.',1,'2022-07-26 17:10:59','2022-07-26 17:10:59'),(6,'What are the benefits of using Olive?','There are numerous benefits of using Olive. First, you can save a good amount of money on your purchase using the coupons on our website or at the store. You can buy a product or avail of the services regularly at a discounted price within the validity period of the coupons, offers, and deals.',1,'2022-07-26 17:11:18','2022-07-26 17:11:18'),(7,'How do I find a store on Olive?','Olive  has 300+ stores and 9000+ coupons and offers on its website. The steps to find a store on Olive are:\r\n1.	Visit the Olive App.\r\n2.	Click on the Categories option at the top right corner of your screen.\r\n3.	Enter your favourite store in the Browse All Categories search bar.\r\n4.	Click on the store option displayed by your search results to see all the upcoming offers and current working coupon codes.',1,'2022-07-26 17:11:47','2022-07-26 17:11:47'),(8,'How to avail offers from Olive?','Users need to follow a few steps to get their products at a cheaper rate by using the coupons obtained from Olive.\r\n1.	Visit our App and enter your desired store in the search bar. You will then see an entire list of the latest offers related to your desired store.\r\n2.     Visit the store and show the olive app offers to related person and enjoy the shopping.\r\n3.	Avail your desired products/services and clear your final bill and the same time try your luck with scan button to scan store QR code and get a chance to grab your free \r\n        return gifts.',1,'2022-07-26 17:14:42','2022-07-26 17:14:42'),(9,'I can\'t find any offers I\'ve seen before. Where did it go?','Olive regularly updates the offers and coupons of all the stores mentioned on its App. So, if you cannot find an offer or a voucher for the available stores on the Olive App, we might have removed that specific offer or a coupon that has already expired or is inapplicable. By doing so, we aim at giving their customers a hassle-free experience, as a result of which the customers can get all the updated offers of all the stores.',1,'2022-07-26 17:18:59','2022-07-26 17:18:59'),(10,'Report a missing store or offer.','To report a missing store or an offer on Olive, you can write to us at info@oliveapp.co.in To get in touch with us with your suggestions and ideas, you can drop a message by entering your full name, email id, and transmission and send it to us. We will get back to you as soon as possible. To get help related to the Olive website/App, you can directly mail us at info@oliveapp.co.in.',1,'2022-07-26 17:19:26','2022-07-26 17:19:26'),(11,'What is the difference between a discount offers & free return gifts?','During the discount , a brand offers a product or products for sale in which it is sold at a much lower price than the actual price. The term discount offers is used by a company to sell its.\r\n              products/goods at a reduced price compared to the original price of the commodity. \r\n\r\nFree return gifts is a personalized set of strings applied to the total bill at the time of checkout. Its so easy to grab, just open your olive app and use scan button to scan store QR code once in a day and get your free return gifts from store side',1,'2022-07-26 17:20:02','2022-07-26 17:20:02'),(12,'How to notify my favorite stores upcoming or current offers?','At Olive, you can select your favorite store and Add with like button so App always show your favorite store offers on top and send notification about store activites.',1,'2022-07-26 17:20:30','2022-07-26 17:20:30'),(13,'What types of free return gifts are there?','There are free return gifts available on specific products and services ,like if you have visited any store and buy product or avail services then you can use scan code button to check your free return gifts offer. Users must also check the terms and conditions of the specific services .Generally, scan codes can be used only once in a day at the time of final bill (terms and conditions apply).',1,'2022-07-26 17:20:56','2022-07-26 17:20:56'),(14,'How do I list my business on Olive?','To list a business on Olive, you can register your self with Sign Up and turn your profile account with business mode that shit and fill your all business details on page .If you find any difficulty to sign up or create business page then feel free to contact us at info@ oliveapp.co.in We will get in touch with you as soon as possible.',1,'2022-07-26 17:21:14','2022-07-26 17:21:14'),(15,'How do my companys discounts and offers appear on Olive?','To submit a offers at Olive, kindly follow the following steps. Visit the Olive App .You may log in with your credentials if you are an existing user. If you are a new user, click on Sign Up and create your account and fill your current offers details correctly on your business page with start to end dates. Click on the Offers section. Submit your Deal simple.',1,'2022-07-26 17:22:16','2022-07-26 17:22:16'),(16,'Does Olive cost me anything?','No, at the Olive App, the users can avail of the benefits of these coupons, discount offers, and deals for free. You can even get the details of the latest upcoming sales and offers for about 250+ stores.',1,'2022-07-26 17:23:00','2022-07-26 17:23:00'),(17,'what is restricted or meaning less on app?','Community users inserting meaningless/useless posts or product reviews will not be entitled to gifts or benefits. Banning such users will be at the sole discretion of Olive management and cannot be challenged.',1,'2022-07-26 17:26:33','2022-07-26 17:26:33'),(18,'why my store not visible no Olive app?','When you make an offer as a seller, only your shop/busines will be shown on the screen. \r\nJust run the offer and it will appear on the screen and disappear if there is no offer. So keep posting your offers and promoting your business yourself.',1,'2022-08-22 17:02:28','2022-08-22 17:02:28');
